{"tid":245609,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五人被控暴動罪　控方庭上突稱影片拍到第四被告　辯方強烈抗議稱是「埋伏」","createTime":"2017-05-16T11:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T00:14:26.000Z","uid":53379,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10f3cd5b05f2e4b9cf2ed6cd7a541625106071fb","tid":245609,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:17:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五人被控暴動罪　控方庭上突稱影片拍到第四被告　辯方強烈抗議稱是「埋伏」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/0516_mk-unrest_a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F0516_mk-unrest_a.jpg&h=1bf2f73d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年農曆年初旺角警民衝突，有五人被控暴動罪的案件今日（十六）在區域法院續審。控方一直指片段沒有拍攝到第四被告孫君和，但在庭上突然指片中有第四被告，辯方律師作出強烈抗議，並投訴這是「trial by ambush」（埋伏），認為播片的手法對證人有引導性。法官也指控方突然用片段指控第四被告是安排不當，加上控方承認未能確定片中人是否第四被告，故法官拒絕讓控方播放該片。聆訊在下午二時半繼續。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五名被告分別是楊子軒、羅浩彥、陳紹鈞、孫君和及連潤發，他們被控三項暴動罪，指他們在去年二月九日於旺角豉油街近花園街交界，連同其他人士參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2017/05/mk-unrest-11/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2017%2F05%2Fmk-unrest-11%2F&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbaS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=b2a65acd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2017/05/mk-unrest-11/</a>"},{"pid":"d4125e252c240e1aa7b643ce4425972c1a02c1f4","tid":245609,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:19:51.000Z","msg":"天佑義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd80589471bb597d218f7fa346536cc2103dcb2","tid":245609,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:21:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天佑義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6371343fac2e068219b963153c55008f7166ce6","tid":245609,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:29:36.000Z","msg":"希望依班信錯兩登及香港人的義士沒事"},{"pid":"73178152483fc791145f666df2da59a338886407","tid":245609,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T15:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34c69b1cba34efa51dab6f7e273bfb3fc3848fb","tid":245609,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T22:42:15.000Z","msg":"香港人仆街唔抵幫 白白犧牲咗"},{"pid":"80bf90a14582b683362a18c5d2e14ea30151ed4e","tid":245609,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T00:14:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人仆街唔抵幫 白白犧牲咗</blockquote><br />\n最仆街就係支那狗<br />\n唔係支那香港依加一定好富強"}]}